75
00:05:06,958 --> 00:05:08,208
What should I--

76
00:05:09,166 --> 00:05:10,708
Lazy, pipsqueak!

77
00:05:10,791 --> 00:05:13,875
I turn around for a second
and you're nappin' on the job?

78
00:05:13,958 --> 00:05:15,458
