that the excitement

89
00:05:45,666 --> 00:05:48,333
you're about to witness
drives you all insane!

90
00:05:48,416 --> 00:05:52,791
So bid your waking life
a fond farewell and prepare

91
00:05:52,875 --> 00:05:54,750
to enter a nightmare!

92
00:05:54,833 --> 00:05:57,208
Let the show begin!

93
00:06:02,125 --> 00:06:03,375
Hey.

94
00:06:06,458 --> 00:06:08,916
--Whoa, hold on.
--Whaddya want?

95
00:06:10,458 --> 00:06:12,000
That a shiner?

96
00:06:12,083 --> 00:06:13,541
You tried to run away,
didn't you?

97
00:06:13,625 --> 00:06:14,250
Leave me alone!

98
00:06:14,333 --> 00:06:15,250
'Ey it's cool.

99
00:06:15,333 --> 00:06:16,750
I'm on your side, kid.

100
00:06:16,833 --> 00:06:19,041
Do you know "As Cinco Horas"?

101
00:06:19,125 --> 00:06:20,625
That's my TV show.

102
00:06:20,708 --> 00:06:22,791
It'll only take one
of my 'special exposés'

103
00:06:22,875 --> 00:06:24,625
to save your poor life.

104
00:06:24,708 --> 00:06:28,000
Now gimme dirt,
and I'll give you this.

105
00:06:28,083 --> 00:06:29,166
What kinda dirt?

106
00:06:29,250 --> 00:06:31,250
Lying, neglect,
physical abuse.

107
00:06:31,333 --> 00:06:33,083
The whole list of
terrible things this circus

108
00:06:33,166 --> 00:06:34,416
has done to you.

109
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:35,750
Abuse?

110
