to your throat, or worse!

118
00:06:49,333 --> 00:06:53,291
Well, thankfully, I, Daniela
Carneiro Junior have found you!

119
00:06:53,375 --> 00:06:56,000
--I'll tell your story!
--None of that is right.

120
00:06:56,083 --> 00:06:59,541
