128
00:07:30,083 --> 00:07:33,333
Did you all get your
beauty sleep last night?

129
00:07:33,416 --> 00:07:34,666
Answer the lady!

130
00:07:34,750 --> 00:07:36,458
Madam Michiko wants
to know if you slept well

131
00:07:36,541 --> 00:07:38,791
--and are ready for pictures!
--Michiko?

132
00:07:38,875 --> 00:07:39,958
Nuno!

133
00:07:41,125 --> 00:07:43,250
Okay, let's get started.

134
00:07:52,250 --> 00:07:54,583
Tell me, child, do you
have any special talents?

135
00:07:54,666 --> 00:07:55,833
Huh-uh.

136
00:07:55,916 --> 00:07:58,041
Well, what have they
got you doin' right now?

137
00:07:58,125 --> 00:08:00,833
