210
00:11:46,041 --> 00:11:46,625
Yes!

211
00:11:46,708 --> 00:11:47,916
Theme park!

212
00:12:31,166 --> 00:12:33,291
Well, I'm back.

213
00:12:33,375 --> 00:12:34,625
