kidnap me again?

222
00:13:01,875 --> 00:13:04,291
Naw, it's not like that.

223
00:13:04,375 --> 00:13:05,500
Then what?

224
00:13:05,583 --> 00:13:07,125
Well, I saw you on
the TV and you looked

225
00:13:07,208 --> 00:13:09,208
so pitiful and depressed.

226
00:13:09,291 --> 00:13:11,458
