239
00:13:38,833 --> 00:13:39,916
Awright, then.

240
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,166
If that's your choice.

241
00:13:41,250 --> 00:13:43,458
Go be with your new Michiko!

242
00:13:52,458 --> 00:13:53,708
Hatchin!

243
00:13:56,833 --> 00:13:58,708
God, I'm an idiot!

244
00:14:05,833 --> 00:14:07,166
What are you doing?

245
00:14:07,250 --> 00:14:08,416
We're leaving now.

246
00:14:08,500 --> 00:14:09,666
Wear this!

247
00:14:12,958 --> 00:14:14,250
While we're young!

248
00:14:14,333 --> 00:14:15,708
Awright, awright!

249
00:14:21,958 --> 00:14:23,500
Ya!

250
00:14:25,208 --> 00:14:26,958
Your hero has returned!

251
00:14:27,041 --> 00:14:29,791
I will not turn
a blind eye to evil!

252
00:14:29,875 --> 00:14:31,916
Here's the proof!

253
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:33,416
Children, I've rescued you!

254
00:14:33,500 --> 00:14:34,875
Follow me!

255
00:14:37,541 --> 00:14:38,166
What?

256
00:14:38,250 --> 00:14:38,833
Uh, hey!

257
00:14:38,916 --> 00:14:39,666
No, stop!

258
00:14:39,750 --> 00:14:41,000
Come back!

259
00:14:41,083 --> 00:14:43,875
Aren't children just
so pure in their instincts?

260
00:14:43,958 --> 00:14:47,125
They can always tell who the
bad guy in the situation is.

261
00:14:47,208 --> 00:14:48,083
You liar!

262
00:14:48,166 --> 00:14:49,625
Kids, don't listen to her!

263
00:14:49,708 --> 00:14:50,708
Fight the power!

264
00:14:50,791 --> 00:14:52,208
Join with me--

265
00:14:53,458 --> 00:14:54,958
Sorry, ace.

266
00:14:59,583 --> 00:15:02,125
Go, Nuno;
get the balloon ready.

267
00:15:02,208 --> 00:15:04,041
We can't take it out
in this kinda weather!

268
00:15:04,125 --> 00:15:05,500
Silence!

269
00:15:05,583 --> 00:15:07,333
You do as I say!

270
00:15:15,458 --> 00:15:16,833
Hatchin.

271
00:15:20,458 --> 00:15:21,708
Awright!

272
00:15:21,791 --> 00:15:22,625
We're all set.

273
00:15:22,708 --> 00:15:24,500
Cut the ropes!

274
00:15:24,583 --> 00:15:26,250
Aye-aye!

275
00:15:26,333 --> 00:15:28,500
My scoop's about
to float away.

276
00:15:28,583 --> 00:15:29,791
I won't let it!

277
00:15:29,875 --> 00:15:32,541
I'm taking you down,
Michiko Menezes!

278
00:15:35,666 --> 00:15:36,666
What'd he say?

279
00:15:38,625 --> 00:15:40,083
That's her?

280
00:15:40,166 --> 00:15:43,125
Michiko?

281
00:15:43,208 --> 00:15:46,083
Oh, Hatchin,
you gotta be shittin' me.

282
00:15:47,875 --> 00:15:50,833
You finally stabbed me in the
heart this time, you know that?

283
00:15:55,833 --> 00:15:56,833
What's happening?

284
00:15:56,916 --> 00:15:58,333
We got too much
weight in the basket!

285
00:15:58,416 --> 00:16:00,375
Well we can't dump
any of the cargo overboard;

286
00:16:00,458 --> 00:16:02,583
we haven't even
gotten paid for 'em yet!

287
00:16:04,041 --> 00:16:05,750
Michiko Menezes!

288
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,250
You vile--

289
00:16:11,166 --> 00:16:14,208
How many times do
we have to go through this?

290
00:16:14,291 --> 00:16:17,875
Now, let's try this again!

291
00:16:20,041 --> 00:16:21,583
Later, sucker!

292
00:16:25,333 --> 00:16:26,791
What the hell
you think yer doin'?

293
00:16:26,875 --> 00:16:28,625
You lied about the theme park!

294
00:16:28,708 --> 00:16:30,791
You're gonna
sell us like slaves!

295
00:16:30,875 --> 00:16:32,333
My, aren't you a smart one.

296
00:16:32,416 --> 00:16:33,208
What the--?

297
00:16:33,291 --> 00:16:35,041
But that won't save you.

298
00:16:35,125 --> 00:16:37,916
You're far too adorable
for me to let go of.

299
00:16:39,708 --> 00:16:41,041
Don't touch her!

300
00:16:41,125 --> 00:16:44,125
No giant piece of carny trash
is stealing my Hatchin!

301
00:16:46,458 --> 00:16:47,250
Who's that?

302
00:16:47,333 --> 00:16:48,375
I dunno.

303
00:16:48,458 --> 00:16:49,958
Michiko!

304
00:16:50,041 --> 00:16:52,791
Hang on, I'm comin'!

305
00:16:52,875 --> 00:16:53,916
This isn't happening.

306
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:55,166
Shoot her, Nuno!

307
00:16:55,250 --> 00:16:56,916
Only tranq darts I got
left are for small game!

308
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:58,416
Just shoot her, you idiot!

309
00:17:01,833 --> 00:17:03,583
Ah! What the hell!

310
00:17:03,666 --> 00:17:05,375
Don't you jack with me!

311
00:17:07,833 --> 00:17:09,416
Who is this crazy broad?

312
00:17:11,250 --> 00:17:12,208
Hatchin!

313
00:17:15,875 --> 00:17:18,625
Michiko!

314
00:17:18,708 --> 00:17:20,875
I'm the only Michiko
that cares about you!

315
00:17:20,958 --> 00:17:22,333
Don't ever forget it!

316
00:17:28,833 --> 00:17:30,750
Nice one!

317
00:17:30,833 --> 00:17:33,458
Bitch, you stole my cargo!

318
00:17:33,541 --> 00:17:35,000
Screw you, bowling ball!

319
00:17:35,083 --> 00:17:36,708
I don't go down that easy.

320
00:17:42,666 --> 00:17:43,875
Michiko!

321
00:17:49,416 --> 00:17:50,708
What do we do now?

322
00:17:50,791 --> 00:17:53,166
If we show up empty-handed,
they're gonna kill us!

323
00:17:53,250 --> 00:17:54,416
Let's just run away!

324
00:17:54,500 --> 00:17:56,125
You ain't runnin' nowhere!

325
00:17:56,208 --> 00:17:57,500
You're still there?

326
00:17:57,583 --> 00:17:59,375
Just give up already!

327
00:18:08,666 --> 00:18:10,083
Michiko!

328
00:18:10,166 --> 00:18:10,625
Get!

329
00:18:10,708 --> 00:18:11,291
Off!

330
00:18:11,375 --> 00:18:11,875
My!

331
00:18:11,958 --> 00:18:12,958
Balloon!

332
00:18:27,666 --> 00:18:28,833
Michiko!

333
00:18:33,083 --> 00:18:34,166
Hatchin?

334
00:18:34,250 --> 00:18:35,375
I took care of them!

335
00:18:35,458 --> 00:18:37,125
Climb up!

336
00:18:37,208 --> 00:18:39,416
Your face looks like shit.

337
00:18:46,750 --> 00:18:48,625
Leggo of me.

338
00:18:48,708 --> 00:18:50,791
We're over the water, right?

339
00:18:50,875 --> 00:18:52,333
I'll be fine.

340
00:18:52,416 --> 00:18:54,708
You're barely conscious!

341
00:18:54,791 --> 00:19:00,375
Hatchin, just lemme fall in.

342
00:19:00,458 --> 00:19:01,875
I'll survive.

343
00:19:01,958 --> 00:19:04,083
Michiko!

344
00:19:09,208 --> 00:19:11,000
You're right, Michiko.

345
00:19:11,083 --> 00:19:12,375
You will be fine.

346
00:19:18,958 --> 00:19:21,458
Because I'm never
letting go of you again.

347
00:19:51,541 --> 00:19:53,125
The scoop is mine!

348
00:20:00,166 --> 00:20:02,000
What happened?

349
00:20:04,708 --> 00:20:06,041
She lives!

350
00:20:07,083 --> 00:20:08,375
Nice day, huh?

351
00:20:09,958 --> 00:20:10,708
Really?

352
00:20:10,791 --> 00:20:12,000
That's all you have to say?

353
00:20:12,083 --> 00:20:13,625
Yeah, what about you?

354
00:20:16,041 --> 00:20:17,708
Already said it.

355
00:20:20,458 --> 00:20:22,041
Fine.

356
00:20:22,125 --> 00:20:24,958
Thanks n' stuff, Hatchin.

357
00:20:25,041 --> 00:20:26,875
Hey, look is
somebody over there?

358
00:20:32,333 --> 00:20:35,333
Well, guess you
owe me one, Michiko.

359
00:20:38,958 --> 00:20:40,958
Hana!

360
00:20:41,041 --> 00:20:42,625
Rita!

361
00:20:42,708 --> 00:20:43,625
Thank God.

362
00:20:43,708 --> 00:20:45,791
I thought you were dead!

363
00:20:45,875 --> 00:20:47,125
Rita?

364
00:20:47,208 --> 00:20:48,666
I thought it was Reba.

365
00:20:48,750 --> 00:20:50,291
What do you care, lady?

366
00:20:52,041 --> 00:20:53,750
Met some kid looking for you.

367
00:20:53,833 --> 00:20:56,750
Glasses, likes
his corned beef?

368
00:20:56,833 --> 00:20:58,125
That your boyfriend?

369
00:20:58,208 --> 00:20:59,833
No! He's gross!

370
00:21:03,416 --> 00:21:04,791
Good bye, Hana.

371
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:09,375
Don't worry,
we'll see each other again.

372
00:21:09,458 --> 00:21:10,541
Soon.

373
00:21:23,125 --> 00:21:24,250
Let's go.

374
00:21:26,916 --> 00:21:28,791
Long road ahead.

